        [
          "You were a huge fan of Phish from the time you went to boarding school.   You ended up dropping out of Bennington to follow them around the country.   You met this great guy at one show and he introduced you to his friends and well...    People often wonder how you reconcile your obviously hippie outlook with your pack's specialty.  But really... it's all about the pack, isn't it?  And it's not like those were-beasts are all sweetness and light, are they? Lots of aggro.  And one thing you've learned over time is that sometimes you need to rise up, right?   Your pride and joy is the Technicolor Dreamboat - the RV you and your packmates use to tool around the country on your hunts.   You maintain it meticulously, make sure Sydney's books are all nicely stacked, that Charlie has all the guns he could ever want, everything.  You know you're not the best fighter.  But you make up for it by handling all the logistics, dealing with the mortals when the need arises, that sort of thing."
